BASKETBALL CHAMPIONSHIPS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA061190-0075 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 232112 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 11, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
